Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.85,0:01:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我最喜歡的髮帶借給劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.12,0:01:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是借給你而已一定要還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.49,0:01:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小熏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.60,0:02:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小姑娘看起來是你的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.07,0:02:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刃衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.94,0:02:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生氣吧生氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.04,0:02:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣你就能回到十年前的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.98,0:02:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恨我吧殺人者拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.58,0:02:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.62,0:02:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刃衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.86,0:02:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七話\N月下之生死決鬥\N為保護所愛的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.27,0:02:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要那麼瞪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又不是捉你來吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.98,0:02:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卑鄙!正大光明的戰鬥\N贏不了劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才把我捉來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.02,0:02:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在抽完一支煙前\N就能把他打倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.79,0:03:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就太無聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你當成人質的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊就會生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.27,0:03:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生氣的傢伙\N就能找回從前的殺人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.64,0:03:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你。你。不知道劍心有多強吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.75,0:03:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.78,0:03:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕府末年的殺人者拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.88,0:03:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有讓人起雞皮疙瘩般的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.56,0:03:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時侯我也在京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新撰組的一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新撰組？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.14,0:03:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刃衛。你的劍沾上了你的血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我們新撰組的恥辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.72,0:03:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分出勝敗來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一樣在京都奮鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.00,0:04:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候的拔刀齊\N差一點就能殺他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.91,0:04:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有趣\N其他的事有這麼有趣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.31,0:04:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心不一樣\N跟只希望流血你不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心不會再成為殺人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿熏？被捉走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.73,0:04:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑笠指定決鬥的場所了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回不來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.74,0:04:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去拜託署長先生把小熏救出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.54,0:04:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那混蛋打算一個人去救阿熏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.88,0:05:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了分出殺人者和殺人者的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人者對殺人者。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.32,0:05:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是劍心已經不是殺人者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他會輸也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.53,0:05:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使這樣那傢伙\N也要一個人去戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.59,0:05:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等！等一下混帳東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我讓我去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在以前發生什麼事我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟幕府末年沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.86,0:05:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去幫助現在的劍心跟阿熏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰在阻止你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你忘了這東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.07,0:05:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走了！章魚不要太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才不要太慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.61,0:06:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就要開始了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.52,0:06:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟那麼有趣的人的時侯開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.66,0:06:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼神很好現在生氣著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.77,0:06:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.67,0:06:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能阻止你\N讓小熏小姐捲進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.85,0:06:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我。。？\N不對這不是平常的劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有很好的殺氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.97,0:07:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下要把\N那奇怪的刀刃翻轉過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.28,0:07:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣\N傳說中的殺人王就復活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.07,0:07:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太狡猾了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.61,0:07:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這。。這是殺人王拔刀齊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.78,0:07:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發怒再發怒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你最厲害的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.25,0:07:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,單手平突擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.22,0:07:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.92,0:07:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.05,0:07:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,橫掃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.92,0:07:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這裏開始是十字型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破竹子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,散掉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.28,0:08:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.82,0:08:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.98,0:08:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡到底在哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.79,0:08:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點找到\N劍心和阿熏都會被作掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.56,0:08:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒有呢\N跟以前的拔刀齊差太遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒有想殺你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.44,0:08:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你倒地後抽三支煙的時候\N再把你殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太無聊了。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.95,0:08:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一點正氣！你真是個魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.55,0:08:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再讓你更生氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.65,0:09:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍。。。心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小熏小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.52,0:09:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你。。對小熏小姐做了什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在她心裏打了一劑強針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.03,0:09:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能讓肺機能麻痹的程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.30,0:09:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過不了五分鐘就窒息死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破這種技術只有二種方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.01,0:10:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一種是被施者\N靠自己的力量解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.55,0:10:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那必須擁有能超越我的劍氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個女人的話就非常不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.46,0:10:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的一種\N得施這種技術的我死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總而言之不把我殺了的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個女人就要死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.51,0:10:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？沒時間了。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.54,0:10:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想看這女人被殺死嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.62,0:10:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刃衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？沒時間了。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.42,0:10:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想看這女人被殺死嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因窒息而死\N那可是非常的難看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刃衛。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.37,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經沒有講話的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要說的話用那把劍來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用那把不正常的刀。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.29,0:11:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現。現在的。不用說劍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.89,0:11:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連身體的動作也看不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.76,0:11:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是飛天御劍流！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.40,0:11:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣殺人拔刀齊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.70,0:11:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩很好很好這種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經沒有講話的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.57,0:11:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會把你給殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.01,0:11:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點放馬過來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍。劍。心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.75,0:11:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要把我殺了嗎\N太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常適合殺人者的台詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於回到原來的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.69,0:11:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個幕府末年！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.66,0:11:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人拔刀齊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.53,0:11:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行。。劍。。心不。。行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.97,0:12:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這裏開始才是真的勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要開始了拔刀齊！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.58,0:12:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是傳說中的殺人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,充滿殺氣後果然不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.89,0:12:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也。。從心裏開始認真起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.16,0:12:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒最強的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.90,0:12:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心之一方是暗示對方\N讓對方驚畏的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.74,0:12:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種技術如果反過來用的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.51,0:12:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是對自己本身的暗示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓自己所有\N潛在的能力發揮出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.95,0:12:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我！不敗也！也！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.39,0:12:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我！無敵！也！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.03,0:13:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我！最強！也！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.40,0:13:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心之一方的技影是「馮鬼之術「
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.34,0:13:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用這個是從新撰組出來後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十五年來的第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是什麼技術\N只要你喜歡就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.26,0:13:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即然你說要殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.97,0:13:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的死也最絕對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.55,0:13:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是！拔刀術的架勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.65,0:13:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在劍術劍套裏猛然拔出\N使其加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.88,0:14:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一瞬間就把對手殺死的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.52,0:14:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這傢伙的拔刀\N是非常的神速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如同神一樣的速度！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放劍過來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.09,0:14:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊的名字的由來\N我會讓你好好的品嚐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.74,0:14:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是拔刀齊一擊必有人死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開後是完全的無防備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.44,0:14:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀的瞬間如果改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是會改變嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.78,0:14:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓它改變吧！讓它改變吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.32,0:14:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是逆刃刀的話\N在拔刀的一瞬間慢了一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會贏的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.26,0:14:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分出勝負吧！拔刀齊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.20,0:14:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.37,0:14:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我贏了！拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.61,0:14:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.38,0:15:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍跟鞘的。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二段拔刀術。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.85,0:15:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流拔刀術「雙龍閃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.49,0:15:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逆刃刀是不適合拔刀術的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.73,0:15:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家知道的非常的清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.30,0:15:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀術的最極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.56,0:15:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是拔刀齊名字的由來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手關節被弄碎了筋也斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.87,0:15:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你使用劍的生命到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你的人生也到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.22,0:15:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊。。劍。。。劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.86,0:15:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.56,0:15:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還在猶豫什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.80,0:15:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要解除那姑娘\N所中的」心之一方」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.04,0:15:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有把我給殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍。。。劍心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.51,0:16:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了救小熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.11,0:16:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再一次的回到殺人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.62,0:16:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說中的殺人的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我刃衛領教看看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.03,0:16:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍是兇器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍術是殺人術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.30,0:16:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼跟漂亮的事比\N那也是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.21,0:16:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是小生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟那事實比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.61,0:16:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如小熏小姐所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.21,0:16:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想法單純來的喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.82,0:16:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍。。劍。。心。。劍心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.96,0:16:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.54,0:17:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要回到殺人者。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人劍。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.24,0:17:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.88,0:17:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.25,0:17:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小熏小姐振作！振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作。。。一點。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.56,0:17:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.00,0:17:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要緊。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.90,0:17:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經不要緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.77,0:17:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到」心之一方」\N也被這小姑娘給破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.78,0:17:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了刃衛單憑那隻小刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.45,0:17:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況只能用左手的傢伙\N已經沒有勝機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.15,0:17:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部結束了乖乖的受綁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.63,0:18:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不還沒結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我來收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.84,0:18:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種感覺真好。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.51,0:18:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要用那種眼神看我。。拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.62,0:18:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說要殺我的時侯\N你的眼神更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.22,0:18:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的本性果然是殺人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.06,0:18:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣是殺人者所說的錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人者終究到死為止\N都要殺人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不能成為其他人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.57,0:18:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說你永遠是流浪人嗎。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.21,0:18:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會在地獄的深處看著你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.96,0:19:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人者終究到死為止\N都要殺人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的就交給警察吧。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.86,0:19:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了！腳印！是劍心的腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.70,0:19:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真。真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.97,0:19:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心的腳印連到這裏來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨。。笨蛋這是牛的腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.98,0:19:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放了我，笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊。阿熏！劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.05,0:19:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧我已經來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏呢！黑笠呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.90,0:19:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是無聊也不等我來救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.80,0:19:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.77,0:19:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我因為整夜鼓勁在干\N現在肚子也餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.74,0:19:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨。。蛋也沒做什麼事\N為什麼會肚子餓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不也是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.97,0:19:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經沒關繫了嗎小熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.21,0:19:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.65,0:20:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！謝謝你救了我。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先跟你道謝一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.05,0:20:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，小生才該跟你道謝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.09,0:20:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼。。？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.73,0:20:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候如果\N小熏小姐不阻止我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.26,0:20:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生就完全返回到\N殺人的拔刀齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.64,0:20:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不勝感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.70,0:20:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？什麼不勝感激呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.47,0:20:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊不。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.34,0:20:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了對了該還你藍色髮帶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.89,0:20:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.12,0:20:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為傷口的血。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.69,0:20:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我最中意的。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.69,0:20:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太過份了\N我們不是約定過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.73,0:20:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對。對不起小熏小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.63,0:20:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛！不要踩我的腳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.47,0:20:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼呢？約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟小孩子無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.97,0:21:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刃衛。。小生的本性是殺人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.84,0:21:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生已不再殺人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.99,0:21:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到死為止都以流浪人而過活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有這些同伴在

